pageContext.claim: “We are really delivering like nobody has, I think, ever delivered before -- if you look back, certainly within the first three years of a presidency. ... But in less than three years, we've done things -- and I always say that I fulfilled more promises than I made, which is a first for a politician.”
pageContext.analysis: According to our Trump Promise Tracker, the president had broken more key promises than he had kept at the conclusion of his third year in office.
